We now examine the quantitative consistency between the rise in temperature (ΔTGMST anomaly in Fig. 1.3) over the AnthropoceneAnthropocene and the radiative forcingradiative forcing of climate attributed to humans (ΔRFradiative forcing in Fig. 1.3). The product 0.31K/Wm−2×2.3Wm−2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
